Per node record (variable-width — offsets.bin tells you where each starts):
  [0:1]   num_layers: uint8
  Per layer:
    [0:2]   neighbour_count: uint16
    [2:2+count*8]  neighbour_slot_ids: uint64 × neighbour_count

Phase 5: write stub records — num_layers=0, no layer data.
